{"tid":289907,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"*日本偽娘喺香港機場女廁偷拍空姐*","createTime":"2017-06-19T11:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T12:45:36.000Z","uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"021622bbdbf607825bd73cf3ebb338a8f425df9e","tid":289907,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"有易服癖好的日籍會計師，今晨(19日)乘機由東京抵港後，聲稱突有易服衝動，便即入殘障人士廁所，並換上一套東京買下女裝，並走入女廁，正好遇上一名剛下班的港龍空姐，空姐見易服的會計師身型魁梧，已感奇怪，未幾發現會計師走入了她旁的廁格如廁，並發現會計師竟伸手將手機伸到空姐廁格內偷拍。會計師今於西九龍法院承認一項不誠實使用電腦罪，被判囚兩星期。<br />\n<br />\n被告Koyanagi Akihiko (36歲)，今於西九龍法院承認一項不誠實使用電腦罪，被判囚兩星期。<br />\n<br />\n居於廣州的日籍會計師被告Koyanagi Akihiko (36歲)承認於2017年6月19日，在香港國際機場一號客運大樓到境大堂的女廁內，不誠實地使用一部黑色Sony手提電話。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情透露，被告與妻育有一名子女，在日本大學畢業後，便到廣州工作，一家人亦居於廣州。被告一直有易服癖好，事發時穿的女裝購自東京，落機後突然有易服想法而犯案。<br />\n被告身型魁梧被識破<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告原定在東京乘搭航班飛抵港後，便轉乘旅遊巴前往廣州工作。惟下機後，他便走到傷殘人士廁所換上女裝，並走入女廁。而女廁此時正有一名剛下班的國泰港龍空姐，空姐見會計師身型魁梧卻穿女裝已感奇怪，但未有理會並走入廁格如廁，會計師見狀後，便走入鄰格，並伸手將手機伸到空姐廁格內偷拍。空姐發現被偷拍後，馬上追上前截停被告及報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員在被告身上檢取到一個黑色假髮、一件黃色外套、粉紅色內衣及一條黑色半截裙。被告在警誡下，換上女裝及偷拍，並表示後悔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/99014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F99014&d=vpd5XgWtkLViUnhvB70SY0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=a9182a99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/99014</a>"},{"pid":"5b49b33a08e9fda2584601d3b96f4f66b7612473","tid":289907,"uid":16871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:17:00.000Z","msg":"無圖點討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891ef626f24c4e045084ba84c7b9d43ec0206db3","tid":289907,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無圖點討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n偽娘都啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce234aa97912684e8f8cd84244a5c7003455d672","tid":289907,"uid":5605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無圖點討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n偽娘都啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n空姐圖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6162fe9bd17f32b36df4e613127e26f5ea39ff0","tid":289907,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"竟然係入不誠實使用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b9fd4473140d5655f194ae1c8fd6148d926f6a","tid":289907,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"Stich"},{"pid":"b3305597c5fd2bc3fc3b14b8ed4730a40a24d4b8","tid":289907,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:30:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d98daa6b1bd0da61904608a57fc4433c8d7bebc","tid":289907,"uid":75470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:34:47.000Z","msg":"今朝落機犯案，今日審今日判埋？"},{"pid":"36d6816f19f2f6251ab0fcc0bc12838ca020cff6","tid":289907,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"不考子 抵拉啦"},{"pid":"a81559eeed84de5e28a7143e4cfb980bf232d91f","tid":289907,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不孝子 抵拉啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"708537e7ec428ae503f7e195fdf66a3e3bae5477","tid":289907,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:43:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86e1435cd5f015363cc89b287bb63fd4f0737220","tid":289907,"uid":43308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:43:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8262cfbe5e04be5085aa345df34538c980e63f00","tid":289907,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8210fcd34a4d6e30e75e5d7b7fade68592833273","tid":289907,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:48:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73ac96dd8cdc56746b754ecbb667c1d2612155e7","tid":289907,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:57:42.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"33b54108e46dd8c1d2f23ee2a2f6cab644da5bfe","tid":289907,"uid":69779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被告在警誡下，換上女裝及偷拍，並表示後悔。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n在警誡下偷拍?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18060c0b5247a96a738d4d430af79f5bafa970c5","tid":289907,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:35:50.000Z","msg":"日狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2f7d61aa64e32d6b76effef67ebfac30ab3c13","tid":289907,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>居於廣州的日籍會計師被告Koyanagi Akihiko (36歲)承認於2017年6月19日，在香港國際機場一號客運大樓到境大堂的女廁內，<span style=\"color: red;\">不誠實</span>地使用一部黑色Sony手提電話。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不誠實？？</blockquote><br />\n任何不懷好意嘅行為都係「dishonest」。英文嘅「dishonest」意思不限於中文嘅「不誠實」, 而係旁及「不正直 / 立心不良」。香港法律先以英文寫成, 後翻譯成中文, 所以咪咁囉。但其實咁樣都無咩問題架, 粵語入面「唔老實」一向都有包括埋「立心不良 / 道德上不可信」嘅意思。所以根本冇問題。</blockquote><br />\nching ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb548996ba7f5b3bb479628d3379216488c4a35","tid":289907,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}